                            "game-id": "6a0bf3cdfe7c0fc427c7b8ea9310f113",
                            "text": "You must physically manipulate an item or make gestures to use an action with this trait. Creatures without a suitable appendage can\u2019t perform actions with this trait. Manipulate actions often trigger reactions."
                        }
                    ],
                    "text": "The pilot engages a lever that activates the clockwork components to launch two massive tethered balloons and fill them with lighter-than-air gas. This grants the flying submersible a fly Speed of 30 but removes its swim Speed. This transformation lasts until the pilot disengages the balloons by performing this action again.",
